{"build_type":"library","description":"As-completed streaming orchestrator: allocates the shared doorbell, the item SPSC queue and the result MPSC array, spawns the producer-runner thread, drives the collector event loop until the stream is closed and every launched worker has completed, returns a {completed:N} JSON. Producer context qrctx is 56 bytes (7 slots): [0..4] queue fields, [6] per-thread arena block carved by provision-worker-arena-block-into-region (de-globalization). Slice 4.4b-1: state[10] now holds a 4096-slot block-ring (allocate-system 32768B) that dispatch fills with each worker's prctx at its spawn slot, for collector-driven gone-edge reaping (design 4.4b).","module_name":"orchestrate-streaming-result-collection-across-spawned-workers","package_name":"orchestrate-streaming-result-collection-across-spawned-workers","function_definitions":{"orchestrate-streaming-result-collection-across-spawned-workers":{"return_type":"i64","parameter_definitions":[{"parameter_name":"q_addr","parameter_type":"i64"},{"parameter_name":"p_addr","parameter_type":"i64"}],"execution_instructions":[{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"seven","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":7},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"zero","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":0},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"one","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":1},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"two","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":2},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"three","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":3},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"four","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":4},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable